|------------|------------------------------------------|
| NodeID     | Unique identifier for each node          |
| NodeName   | Name of the file or folder               |
| ParentID   | Parent folder NodeID (NULL if root)      |
| SizeBytes  | Size in bytes (NULL if it's a folder)    |

</span><span><span class="hljs-section">## 🧮 Objective</span></span><span>
To calculate the total size of every folder (including all nested children) using recursive SQL queries.

</span><span><span class="hljs-section">## 🧪 Sample Output</span></span><span>
